sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VLLMPod as KServe Predictor Pod<br/>(vllm-rocm container)
    participant VLLM as vLLM Engine<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as AMD GPU<br/>ROCm/HIP
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>S3/PVC 443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup
    VLLMPod->>Storage: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: IAM / SA token
    Storage-->>VLLMPod: Model artifacts
    VLLMPod->>GPU: Load model to GPU memory<br/>HIP runtime
    GPU-->>VLLMPod: Model loaded

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / kube-rbac-proxy
    Ingress->>VLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP plaintext (cluster-internal)
    VLLM->>GPU: Execute inference<br/>HIP runtime
    GPU-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
    VLLM-->>Ingress: JSON Response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS-compatible)
    Client->>Ingress: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+
    Ingress->>TGIS: Forward request<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP plaintext (cluster-internal)
    TGIS->>VLLM: Internal call to vLLM engine
    VLLM->>GPU: Execute inference<br/>HIP runtime
    GPU-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
    VLLM-->>TGIS: Token stream
    TGIS-->>Ingress: gRPC stream response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS streamed response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: Caikit via TGIS Adapter
    participant Caikit as caikit-tgis-serving
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC 8033/TCP<br/>plaintext (cluster-internal)
    TGIS->>VLLM: Internal call
    VLLM->>GPU: Inference
    GPU-->>VLLM: Tokens
    VLLM-->>TGIS: Response
    TGIS-->>Caikit: gRPC response
